{
  "stem": "22047.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I knew that-- that folks were being killed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, I-- I certainly wanted to survive to an old age.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I think we mentioned this earlier, I-- I have a lot of faith.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had a lot of faith then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I figured, I'm going to make it through.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- I I'm pretty-- pretty smart, militarily, and I know-- know how to use a weapon.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I am, I think, a leader, and I know how to lead men.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I've-- I felt comfortable in that regard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so I-- I obviously apprehensive and a bit afraid, as I think everybody was who faced combat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I didn't want to-- didn't want to look at the Statue of Liberty when we shipped out because I thought, you know, some weeks hence, we're going to go into combat.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I just don't-- I felt, I guess, a lonesomeness of homesickness maybe, leaving our country and going to a strange places that I'd never seen before.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How am I going to react when I get there?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Am I going to be [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so afraid that I'll be a coward when I get there?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't think I would, because I-- I-- I have a lot of-- of self confidence, or had then, I think, from various aspects of my civilian and my military background.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did you feel any resentment that you have to go fight for--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "None at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was really fighting for the United States, although, of course, we were over there to help France and the British and the Dutch and everybody else, that we're fighting for them, but we're also fighting for the United States, and we're fighting against the Japanese directly.",
      "word_count": 47
    }
  ],
